{"id":438099,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":12,"day":4}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"180","ytitle":"","mtitle":"古巴好比傲霜菊","ftitle":"","authors":["田宝玉"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"田宝玉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花喜鹊，叫喳喳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新娶的嫂嫂剪窗花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光的剪子手中舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪白的毛巾头上搭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不剪牡丹争富贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不剪清水戏白鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单剪一枝傲霜菊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风雨把根扎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“英雄才配英雄花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹花香送千家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非哥哥立了功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不剪它为什么?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂脸儿一阵红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂声丫头瞎猜哒:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傲菊送到古巴去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插在首都哈瓦那。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹不败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨打不垮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨越大花越发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴好比傲霜菊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映起满天红彩霞。"}]}